  "texts": [
    "35 have proposed a ToM-based human intention validation model for the robotized warehouse.",
    "The suggested mechanism effectively validated the motion of the workers according to the target location by generalized Voroni procedure.",
    "Different calculations were executed in the developed framework through a hidden Markov technique to validate the intention of the worker.",
    "The scalability of the developed framework was contrasted over several metrics to compute the robustness over the conventional mechanism.",
    "36 have presented a new robotic system to monitor two different working modes such as human-active and robot-active mode."
